items.name: Silento-Emergency-Alert-
items.description: Silento is a silent emergency alert system that uses gesture-based triggers (like blinking) to detect danger and send the user’s live location to a trusted contact via email. Built with Python, it ensures quick, discreet alerts without physical interaction—ideal for safety and health emergencies.
